{"tid":640943,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《黑寡婦》電影係同寒冬戰士有關？","createTime":"2018-04-24T15:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T03:19:25.000Z","uid":105567,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e829826517ca332339033729893f6b80e2c00fcc","tid":640943,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=26463&amp;catid=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Farticles%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D26463%26catid%3D21&d=XmPZqPdg3dAFg8b49juXyJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0b3c85b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=26463&amp;catid=21</a><br />\n<br />\n黑寡婦做主角嘅個人電影喺早幾個月終於獲得確認，新片屬黑寡婦Natasha Romanoff前傳故事，但就唔會關於《復仇者聯盟》內Natasha提到做神盾局特工時期與鷹眼Clint Barton於布達佩斯進行嘅秘密任務，而係《鐵甲奇俠2》前Natasha於美國生活嘅一段故事。<br />\n據報當時蘇聯垮台15年，Natasha同寒冬戰士Bucky相遇嘅故事，Bucky仍然係受命於Hydra擔任殺手，而漫畫中亦有相當多關於兩人相遇嘅情節。《黑寡婦》電影劇本由Jac Schaeffer負責編寫，而目前Marvel尚未公布導演人選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zDm0FjjmW7o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzDm0FjjmW7o&d=XmPZqPdg3dAFg8b49juXyJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b4fbe7e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zDm0FjjmW7o</a>"},{"pid":"d347d0ab8b46346af39129113cb9a0ed9f006faa","tid":640943,"uid":105567,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/0a8be4a94fdd7f2ed1dd747b4b175ccf/tumblr_inline_o6n3mklMHt1s8q874_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F0a8be4a94fdd7f2ed1dd747b4b175ccf%2Ftumblr_inline_o6n3mklMHt1s8q874_500.gif&h=c92d4758&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bba9014f21e3e7b681368aca6c71b0bd477858a","tid":640943,"uid":7814,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"d347d0ab8b46346af39129113cb9a0ed9f006faa","tid":640943,"uid":105567,"like":13,"dislike":1,"scor